data.description: Berkshire Pines is tucked away in the quaint community of Berkshire Lakes, you'll find beautiful Florida Pines, preserves, beauty and an updated clubhouse with a large pool and many amenities!! This beautiful villa has a brand new tankless water heater, new refrigerator, new base boards and new Coretec flooring throughout!! The A/C has an ultra violet light for fresh air and the A/C ducts were recently sealed!! Accordion hurricane panels and clear hurricane panels on all windows!! Enjoy nice Florida winter evenings on the 24ft wide screened in lanai with a roof!! The property is nice and bright with a lot of open space in the 22 X 16 Great Room!! The entire inside was recently painted!! The clubhouse has a playground, large pool and patio!! Three minutes to Publix and restaurants!! Only 15mins to the beach!! Yard maintenance is included in the association fees!
